&lt;p&gt;Some toasters are overrated. This may be one of them. It is unlike any other, I&amp;rsquo;ll give it that, it has a conveyor belt that moves the bread past coiled heating elements. It works medium well, and is very mechanically complex. Overall, I&amp;rsquo;d give it a &amp;ldquo;great innovation, but lacking&amp;rdquo; out of 10. It&amp;rsquo;s cool as hell though.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>